project_name: * The Experiment/Project Identifcation number, identifies each experiment and the samples it owns.
sample_name: * Sample Identification Number, uniquely identifies each sample within an experiment
samp_store_loc: * The storage location of the sample
material: The material displaced by the sample when taken
samp_type: The primary type classification (liquid, solid, gaseous)
geo_loc_name: The description of the latitude and longitude
notes: Any notes / extra observations and fields
source_subject_id: The identification number of the source from which the sample came from
source_name_primary: The primary type classification of the source
source_name_secondary: The secondary type classification of the source
source_treatment: The treatment of the source pertaining to the experiment (diet, controls, etc)
